resourcePool.intro: The Physiotherapy Clinic at SPORTSCO is run by Colette O’Flynn, B. Physio, M.I.S.C.P., Lic. Ac.  A chartered physiotherapist by profession, Colette was educated at University College, Dublin, the Royal National Hospital for Rheumatic Diseases in Bath, England and the British College of Acupuncture and Herbal Medicine.  She spent ten years with Dublin’s Mater Misericordiae Hospital and was the Physiotherapist In Charge of the Mater’s renowned Hydrotherapy Department. Her work has been featured on RTÉ television, and in the national press.  Her corporate clients include some of the most prestigious companies in the country, including ESB, RTÉ and Irish Life. SPORTSCO offers a full on-site physiotherapy service, including manual therapy, electrotherapy, acupuncture, dry needling, exercise prescription, one-to-one pilates and rehab exercise programmes.
resourcePool.name: Physiotherapy
resourcePool.notes: The Clinic has a range of chartered physiotherapists offer a full range of physiotherapy and sports injury treatments to both members and non-members. For appointments and bookings with Colette O’Flynn, please call her directly on 086-8342525.
